{"tid":1295691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「FUCK THE POLICE」challenge正式開始","createTime":"2019-07-08T06:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T08:04:29.000Z","uid":36797,"like":55,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"eee6b13e7ec3d7d969b582f2e7dab233a0dbbd0c","tid":1295691,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:01:53.000Z","msg":"岩岩開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIG story用你最有創意既做法與黑警展開激情對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本要求：錄/寫句「屌你老母黑警」<br />\n然後你可以打文/拍片同佢地講道理<br />\n你可以問下佢地做狗咩感覺<br />\n你可以post相出黎同佢地理論點解咁做都合理<br />\n你可以改歌唱埋擺出黎又得<br />\n你可以拍低自己鋪頭外面張「警察與狗不得內進」<br />\n你可以錄低打小人<br />\n你可以post自己屌緊差佬老婆既片<br />\n運用你地啲創意！<br />\n<br />\n留低對黑警既感覺，用唔同方法將黑警既惡行宣揚出去。低智黑警愈燥，愈會做出啲戇鳩行為。<br />\n最緊要最後tag 3個朋友接力，加個#fuckthepolicechallenge喺最尾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我見到ig有朋友開始左，我幫佢share上黎等多啲人知。<br />\n遍地開花呀各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c1ace181d54dceba3e2a0547232ba8ad3b16b8","tid":1295691,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c1fb367e54bb9a600728ab95964048d7fac593","tid":1295691,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"同佢講英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cc54607d307c9894718f4bb773f6e24abe1b3c","tid":1295691,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"[英文速譯] 綜合大量警察嚴重違規行為<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295342</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a3583c085402fbd5d7c47d83520a38ebb1565f0","tid":1295691,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" cla